giz week 2 challenge
====================

dependencies: rust, uv

run the program:

```
cargo run --release # synchronous thread-per-connection model
cargo run --release --features async-rt # single-threaded asynchronous tokio-backed model
```

run the benchmark

```
uv run benchmark.py
```

